              <p>We ran our program with different values for the weight <italic>w</italic> and length ℓ of the spaced words for different numbers of patterns and for different values of the threshold <italic>T</italic>. Here, we modified the value of one of these parameters at a time and used the default values for the remaining three parameters. Default values of the modified parameters and the resulting runtimes and RF distances are shown in bold font.</p>
