  <sec id="sec11">
    <title>Author contributions</title>
    <p>C.A.L. designed the study, co-supervised the project, and drafted parts of the manuscript. J.S. implemented the software and did most of the program evaluation. S.D. contributed to the program evaluation. M.G. and C.B. analyzed and discussed the results on <italic>Wolbachia</italic> and wrote parts of the manuscript. B.M. co-supervised the project and wrote most of the manuscript.</p>
